WEBVTT
Kind: captions
Language: en

00:00:00.160 --> 00:00:01.714
Hey, good morning, family.

00:00:01.714 --> 00:00:02.879
Praise the Lord.

00:00:02.879 --> 00:00:07.368
Day 48—we're almost to 50, Braden.

00:00:09.159 --> 00:00:13.716
It's a celebration: 50 videos, not in a row but close.

00:00:14.391 --> 00:00:18.074
We just want to say thank you all for joining us today.

00:00:18.555 --> 00:00:24.320
For all the new people, if this is your first video and you've never been here before, welcome.

00:00:24.495 --> 00:00:29.530
Welcome to all the faithful people who have been here for so long; we really appreciate it.

00:00:29.530 --> 00:00:35.507
If you could like the video, subscribe if you haven't, and click the notification bell.

00:00:35.507 --> 00:00:38.529
It would really bless us and help us with the algorithm.

00:00:38.724 --> 00:01:01.857
It truly does help us every time I say something silly and you start commenting on it; it boosts that thing way up in the algorithm.

00:01:01.857 --> 00:01:28.680
We laugh about it because Braden says, 'Hey, I'm glad you messed up today, Dad, because it helped our video,' since he watches all the analytics.

00:01:29.436 --> 00:01:38.885
I don't understand all that, but he's really smart.

00:01:38.885 --> 00:01:59.640
I've had a lot of emails—Diana says we've had a lot of emails—wanting to know about the Five Pillars.

00:01:59.640 --> 00:02:29.919
Ladies and gentlemen, I've had people who are not very educated about crypto jump into something they don't know and then say, 'Well, you told me to do it.

00:02:29.919 --> 00:02:42.240
' I've never told anybody to do anything; I'll stick by that.

00:02:44.502 --> 00:02:47.886
I am not a financial advisor.

00:02:50.339 --> 00:03:04.480
I tell you what I feel the Lord has told me about crypto, gold, silver, and land.

00:03:04.480 --> 00:03:24.253
He talks to me about all kinds of things, but rarely about stocks.

00:03:24.253 --> 00:03:44.233
Every so often He will, but I'm not here to advise you on your finances.

00:04:01.527 --> 00:04:02.680
I know some people understand that, but there are some who just don't.

00:04:02.680 --> 00:04:07.822
This is for entertainment purposes only.

00:04:07.822 --> 00:04:21.000
I am not telling you to buy, sell, or do anything.

00:04:21.000 --> 00:04:23.000
This is my opinion, and I'm entitled to it.

00:04:24.493 --> 00:05:08.000
I believe in what the Lord has told me, and I say you should go out and pray, asking the Holy Spirit what He wants you to do with your finances.

00:05:08.000 --> 00:05:39.144
Do not invest in something unless you're educated, and do not do anything with your money until the Holy Spirit tells you to.

00:05:39.144 --> 00:05:55.199
It's very important you know this; what I pray about might not be for you.

00:06:12.919 --> 00:06:13.391
Everybody's walk is different.

00:06:13.391 --> 00:06:20.999
Whenever I'm talking about the Five Pillars, I saw five major cryptocurrencies that will be the pillars of all crypto.

00:06:20.999 --> 00:06:35.810
There will be five: three are very strong, and there's one that's the strongest.

00:06:36.618 --> 00:06:53.809
I saw one in the middle, two on the side of it, and then two more over.

00:06:54.822 --> 00:07:07.560
They were standing like Greek or Roman columns made of solid granite.

00:07:18.179 --> 00:07:36.170
The Holy Spirit showed me support systems on these columns, which were other cryptocurrencies that line up with the functions of those main ones.

00:07:36.170 --> 00:07:48.879
There were probably five or so helping each main coin, propping it up.

00:07:48.879 --> 00:08:19.208
Then I saw falling stars—all the other cryptos that had no real function, which I would call scams, started falling like internet code and ceased to exist.

00:08:19.208 --> 00:08:26.880
Thousands of them disappeared in the vision.

00:08:26.880 --> 00:08:32.055
Then I heard 'governmental regulations.

00:08:32.055 --> 00:09:03.993
' I saw bills being passed to make it stable because I heard 'Wild West,' and laws were being brought into motion to protect investors so they would not be scammed.

00:09:03.993 --> 00:09:30.046
They were going to regulate it, and then I saw 'old money'—the elderly people with big money—starting to put their money in because they felt safe.

00:09:30.046 --> 00:09:37.819
Right now, it's the Wild West with no laws.

00:09:37.819 --> 00:10:00.413
Look at all the stuff that has happened even before Donald Trump has been sworn into office.

00:10:00.413 --> 00:10:06.380
It is like a rocket ship.

00:10:11.071 --> 00:10:19.920
You can see the 5, 4, 3, 2, 1, and the smoke before liftoff.

00:10:19.920 --> 00:10:50.880
He's not even in office yet, but everyone is anticipating who he's going to put as the head of the SEC who is pro-crypto.

00:11:03.635 --> 00:11:08.853
I don't follow all this stuff; I just pray, and the Lord gives me visions.

00:11:08.853 --> 00:11:29.559
However, that doesn't mean it's for today or even five years from now; I don't know the time frame.

00:11:29.559 --> 00:11:58.544
Braden and I were looking at when Kim Clement gave his word about XMP and all the things the Lord showed him; that was 12 or 13 years ago.

00:12:00.355 --> 00:12:24.112
If people tried to figure out what XMP was back then, they would have been disappointed when the lawsuit came in and it went down to 15 cents.

00:12:24.112 --> 00:12:28.480
XMP was what it was.

00:12:32.726 --> 00:12:42.940
You have prophetic words given by people who see in the spirit, but you never know the timing.

00:12:42.940 --> 00:12:49.833
There is depth perception to the prophetic.

00:12:49.833 --> 00:13:02.570
You don't know when that 'oak tree' is coming to pass.

00:13:02.570 --> 00:13:24.299
As of right now, that word has still not fully manifested or hit the all-time high he was talking about.

00:13:28.503 --> 00:13:45.496
You have to use discernment and wisdom, not just get on a 'Holy Ghost bandwagon' listening to men on the internet.

00:13:50.048 --> 00:13:56.745
You have to hear it inside yourself because it is volatile.

00:13:58.289 --> 00:14:05.742
It goes up and down, and it freaks me out.

00:14:05.742 --> 00:14:17.220
Who knows if it will fall by a dollar or ten?

00:14:17.980 --> 00:14:27.137
You must know the Holy Spirit is leading you.

00:14:27.137 --> 00:14:44.564
My son was showing me that everybody, their brother, and their dog is prophesying about XMP and other things.

00:14:44.564 --> 00:15:11.025
There is a ton of prophetic work out there, and I'm not dogging them—who am I to say anything about those people?

00:15:11.025 --> 00:15:20.423
—but you have to be very discerning.

00:15:28.093 --> 00:15:50.880
You might be hearing something out of the flesh just because 'Billy Bob' said it and you want to make a viral video too.

00:15:50.880 --> 00:15:56.789
There are 'bandwagon prophets' out there.

00:15:56.789 --> 00:16:10.610
I saw five main things, and I saw regulation coming in.

00:16:23.600 --> 00:16:23.950
I saw stability and increase.

00:16:31.719 --> 00:16:48.320
The Lord said to me, 'The very thing the body of Christ is trying to embrace right now is the very thing that leads to the mark of the beast.

00:16:48.320 --> 00:17:13.754
' A cashless society is part of the end-time system; it's the technology behind what's coming with the chip, and none of you are going to want that.

00:17:13.754 --> 00:17:23.539
There's just so much to it in the spirit realm.

00:17:23.539 --> 00:17:33.360
Would I like to tell you about the other four pillars?

00:17:33.360 --> 00:17:40.220
Yes, my heart would love to, but I can't.

00:17:40.590 --> 00:17:54.811
If I go into all that, you'll put all your money into them.

00:17:54.811 --> 00:18:10.120
I've already gotten emails from people saying they put their life inheritance in.

00:18:10.120 --> 00:18:16.750
Why would you do that?

00:18:16.750 --> 00:18:23.160
Only do what you can afford if the Lord tells you to.

00:18:40.253 --> 00:18:52.368
I work too hard for my money; I know how much it takes to sell stuff on eBay to pay an electric bill.

00:18:59.624 --> 00:19:23.210
If you put money into crypto, you have to look at it like going to the movies or buying fireworks—that money is gone once it's spent.

00:19:34.599 --> 00:19:42.084
I know what the Lord has shown me, but we are just imperfect vessels.

00:19:42.084 --> 00:20:01.658
Pure water can come from the Father, but if it comes through a tainted pipe, the water becomes tainted.

00:20:01.658 --> 00:20:13.669
You have to watch what you're hearing on the internet.

00:20:14.819 --> 00:20:31.506
I have compassion for folks, but there are desperate people doing dumb things.

00:20:31.506 --> 00:20:52.737
I've had family members say they are going to put advances on their credit cards.

00:20:52.737 --> 00:21:04.760
Hold on a minute; that's not God.

00:21:04.760 --> 00:21:13.600
God is not a god of debt.

00:21:13.600 --> 00:21:29.240
He said to owe no man anything but to love him.

00:21:31.740 --> 00:21:39.620
I do not believe in borrowing money on credit cards.

00:21:39.620 --> 00:22:11.420
If you have a car note or a house payment to have a nice home, that's one thing, but borrowing with high interest rates is a trap that keeps you from being free.

00:22:11.420 --> 00:22:16.488
If God doesn't provide it, I don't need it.

00:22:16.488 --> 00:22:33.891
He's going to give us creative ideas to get wealth and revelation knowledge.

00:22:48.200 --> 00:22:48.880
I believe if you sow a seed, you'll reap a harvest.

00:22:55.500 --> 00:22:55.840
I believe more in that than anything.

00:22:55.840 --> 00:23:13.600
God provides for His kids, and it's not a chance thing; it's seedtime and harvest.

00:23:13.600 --> 00:23:28.940
Reaping is a law just as much as sowing is.

00:23:41.413 --> 00:23:51.143
I believe in the hundredfold return and that the Lord will bless our hands to prosper.

00:23:51.143 --> 00:24:04.440
I believe in that more than any kind of crypto.

00:24:04.440 --> 00:24:32.697
There was so much talk about the dinar for years, or network marketing pyramid schemes promising you'll be rich.

00:24:32.697 --> 00:24:55.240
There's nothing inherently wrong with network marketing, but often you get to the top and they promise so much.

00:25:02.835 --> 00:25:36.154
I remember people at church always trying to do network marketing; you'd try to avoid them in the hall because you knew they'd try to sell you Amway.

00:25:36.154 --> 00:26:06.550
Many people have contacted me to do network marketing on this platform, asking me to sign up under them and promote it to you all.

00:26:06.550 --> 00:26:28.933
I've told you: I am not going to sell anything to anybody on this channel.

00:26:34.245 --> 00:26:40.799
I will never ask you for money.

00:26:42.332 --> 00:27:01.293
I put my merch on there because people asked for it, but I don't even promote it.

00:27:01.293 --> 00:27:13.420
This channel will always be about Jesus Christ and His coming.

00:27:13.420 --> 00:27:23.510
It's never going to be a crypto channel.

00:27:23.510 --> 00:27:48.066
My heart is to tell you that He's coming soon and you need to get your house in order.

00:27:48.066 --> 00:28:12.440
I had more to talk about today, but that took too much time.

00:28:12.440 --> 00:28:44.590
Tomorrow I'll tell you about the man who flew from Australia to Oklahoma to warn me about a vision I had of an EMP attack on America.

00:28:44.590 --> 00:29:13.383
He felt the Holy Spirit told him to warn me about a Chinese company that bought a grain refinery on the Mississippi River.

00:29:24.755 --> 00:29:38.506
I told you all about a barge floating up the Mississippi River that was owned by a Chinese company.

00:29:40.185 --> 00:29:58.485
The government tried to stop the sale, but the state sold it anyway.

00:29:58.485 --> 00:30:28.559
This barge I saw coming down the Mississippi went out into the Gulf and had a rocket on it that said 'USSR.

00:30:28.559 --> 00:30:56.624
' When they shot it over America, it didn't get high enough, and the EMP only affected areas like Kentucky.

00:30:56.624 --> 00:31:21.404
This was a vision of a surprise attack from Asian people—I don't know if they were Chinese or North Korean.

00:31:30.815 --> 00:31:31.790
The Lord told me they were coming for grains.

00:31:31.790 --> 00:31:52.680
Seeing this company buy a grain refinery on the Mississippi sent alarm bells off inside me.

00:31:52.680 --> 00:32:13.794
It's not a coincidence; it's like a Trojan surprise attack from the Gulf of Mexico.

00:32:13.794 --> 00:32:20.705
It's something to pray about.

00:32:20.705 --> 00:32:47.456
If you study enough, the Five Pillars are pretty obvious, but the safe way is to let the Holy Spirit show you.

00:32:47.456 --> 00:32:58.120
Father, I thank You for every person here.

00:32:58.120 --> 00:33:25.091
I thank You that no weapon formed against them shall prosper and that they would have wisdom in what to invest in.

00:33:25.091 --> 00:33:43.508
Let them follow the voice of the Holy Spirit, not a trend or a fad.

00:33:43.508 --> 00:33:56.695
I ask that they have ears to hear.

00:34:12.130 --> 00:34:12.500
We take authority over hype and all demonic attacks from scammers.

00:34:20.759 --> 00:34:28.383
We thank You, Lord, that the body of Christ will be protected.

00:34:51.479 --> 00:34:51.919
You are our Shepherd; You lead us beside still waters and restore our souls.

00:34:56.286 --> 00:35:08.135
We take authority over the demonic spirits trying to come against President Trump.

00:35:08.135 --> 00:35:37.463
We thank You that he is protected—that a thousand shall fall at his side and ten thousand at his right hand, but nothing shall come near him.

00:35:37.463 --> 00:35:55.855
We thank You that his family is protected and that any plans of the wicked will be uncovered.

00:36:09.215 --> 00:36:10.065
We cover the vice presidency and RFK Jr.

00:36:11.590 --> 00:36:30.725
in the blood of Jesus as he works to bring out the evil in the Food and Drug Administration.

00:36:38.067 --> 00:36:46.875
We thank You that there will be justice for the seeds of evil sown in the past.

00:36:50.060 --> 00:37:01.480
We claim back sevenfold everything the devil stole.

00:37:01.480 --> 00:37:19.968
We call for restitution—not just in finances, but in time and health.

00:37:19.968 --> 00:37:40.749
Just as You delivered the children of Israel out of Egypt, You will deliver Your people now.

00:37:40.749 --> 00:37:54.960
We call for financial increase and sweatless victories.

00:37:54.960 --> 00:38:04.095
We are debt-free, the head and not the tail.

00:38:04.095 --> 00:38:28.319
We plead the blood of Jesus over every negative seed we've sown in ignorance and call for crop failure on those bad seeds.

00:38:28.319 --> 00:38:45.720
Every seed produces after its own kind; how you treat people is a seed.

00:38:45.720 --> 00:38:50.940
Seedtime and harvest will never cease.

00:38:53.217 --> 00:39:05.707
We thank You, Father, for the hostages to be released in Israel.

00:39:05.707 --> 00:39:15.079
We pray for the peace of Jerusalem.

00:39:15.079 --> 00:39:36.660
We thank You that all darkness is exposed in that camp and that the innocent Palestinian children and women are protected.

00:39:38.245 --> 00:40:02.665
We thank You for the oil and gas wealth about to spring forth in Israel and for a fresh breath on the Abrahamic Covenant.

00:40:02.665 --> 00:40:13.180
We ask for protection for Trump until he is sworn in.

00:40:13.180 --> 00:40:27.960
We thank You that all evil plans of the current administration will be uncovered.

00:40:31.675 --> 00:40:49.860
I told you that eventually, America, Canada, and Mexico would have a digital currency joined as three nations.

00:40:49.860 --> 00:41:01.467
Trump already told Trudeau he has a plan for that.

00:41:01.467 --> 00:41:16.486
He knows what's going on with the BRICS nations and the dollar.

00:41:20.695 --> 00:41:26.266
Father, give him Solomon-like wisdom to lead this nation.

00:41:26.266 --> 00:41:50.810
We thank You that corruption will be uncovered in the House and Senate and that godly leaders will rise up.

00:41:50.810 --> 00:41:59.920
We pray for Elon Musk to be born again and filled with the Holy Spirit.

00:42:18.703 --> 00:42:19.171
We call forth the laborers to bring in the lost.

00:42:30.611 --> 00:42:39.265
We call for revival over Asia, South Korea, China, and the underground church.

00:42:39.265 --> 00:42:52.440
We pray for revival in Venezuela, Cuba, Jamaica, and all the islands.

00:43:07.780 --> 00:43:08.160
We call for revival in Africa, England, Europe, Australia, and Queensland.

00:43:08.160 --> 00:43:20.119
Stir the hearts of the preachers to be bold.

00:43:25.919 --> 00:43:32.516
We praise You for a new hunger and thirst after righteousness.

00:43:43.359 --> 00:43:43.644
We call marriages restored and bodies healed.

00:43:54.369 --> 00:43:54.744
Thank you for joining me today.

00:44:02.125 --> 00:44:08.472
I appreciate all the support and kindness during this Christmas season.

00:44:10.148 --> 00:44:11.794
Happy Birthday, Jesus!

00:44:11.794 --> 00:44:19.137
He is my Lord and Savior.

00:44:19.754 --> 00:44:24.065
We always have a cake for Him as a family and sing Happy Birthday.

00:44:31.532 --> 00:44:34.092
Some might think that's silly, but He loves it.

00:44:34.092 --> 00:44:52.060
If you make a place for Him in your house, He'll visit you.

00:45:11.769 --> 00:45:12.219
Come to Him as a child, not an adult.

00:45:16.089 --> 00:45:30.160
He is the Lord of the Harvest, and all He cares about is your heart.

00:45:30.160 --> 00:45:48.684
He died for you and rose again so you wouldn't have to go through hell.

00:45:48.684 --> 00:46:04.879
I've seen the holes in His hands and feet; He did it all for you.

00:46:13.220 --> 00:46:13.400
All you have to do is receive it by faith.

00:46:13.400 --> 00:46:20.485
Put a smile on your face and a song in your heart.

00:46:20.485 --> 00:46:34.226
Jesus loves you so much, and we will see you again tomorrow.

00:46:34.226 --> 00:46:36.128
Bye-bye.
